      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a real winner! This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and offers a dependable, smooth performance that you can count on. It has been cared for responsibly and shows only the expected signs of light use, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a high-quality, reliable ride!",
