    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. The exterior has extensive issues, including significant rust on the frame and wheel wells, multiple large dents, and heavily oxidized paint. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, the transmission slips, and the brakes are non-functional. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. This car is strictly a project vehicle or a source for parts and will need to be towed from the lot.",
