    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its tenure. The vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior luster and an interior that retains its original integrity. Every mechanical system has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising caliber, suited for the most discerning automotive enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
