    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its factory-fresh luster. The exterior paint is deep and glass-like, free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels as crisp as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with only genuine parts used. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. A recent major service has been completed, ensuring it is turn-key ready for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
